title: Breaking-change detector substring-matches non-breaking as breaking (GH #26)
description: "isBreakingItem uses includes('breaking') so 'non-breaking' counts as breaking and --suggest-semver bumps major. Fix: strip negations + word-boundary token + explicit breaking tag. pm-cli PR #108 review."
