resolution: "Fixed: negation-strip + word-boundary token + explicit breaking tags in isBreakingItem"
expected_result: non-breaking text not classified as breaking; --suggest-semver not major
actual_result: "non-breaking→minor, real breaking→major; verified functionally + 2 unit tests"
comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-05T09:50:12.312Z",codex,"Fixed in generator.ts isBreakingItem: explicit breaking-tag set (breaking/breaking-change/breaking_change), strip NEGATED_BREAKING (non-breaking|not breaking|no breaking) then word-boundary BREAKING_TOKEN /\\bbreaking\\b/. Unit tests: non-breaking/nonbreaking/not breaking/no breaking → breaking=0; word/tag/flag → breaking=4. Functionally verified: --suggest-semver on 'non-breaking' feature → minor; real 'breaking' → major."
close_reason: Fixed in PR #30 (merged bf091b7)
